cad-viewer — STEP / IGES / BREP support
========================================

This extension bundles `occt-import-js` — an emscripten interface to
OpenCASCADE — which parses STEP / IGES / BREP files into a Three.js-compatible
mesh, entirely in the browser via WebAssembly.

  occt-import-js:  https://github.com/kovacsv/occt-import-js
  OpenCASCADE:     https://www.opencascade.com

